+ AJAX(Asynchronous JavaScript And XML) is a set of Web development techiques using many web
technologies on the client side to create asychronous Web applications.
	-why we need AJAX
+ Load on the webpage without refresh
+ website behieve like the desktop application
+ Request and Receive data from a server - after the page has loaded 
+ Send data to server - in the background

